# Architecture

- All string literals (command IDs, config keys, view IDs) live in `constants.ts` — never hardcode them
- Config reads/writes go through `services/configService.ts` — never call `getConfiguration()` directly
- `CypressRunner` owns test execution; `TestExplorer` owns UI orchestration
- Use `ShellExecution` options for env vars, not string concatenation
- Webviews must have a CSP with a nonce
- See `ROADMAP.md` for the full improvement plan
